channel.title: How to make a good gameframe?
channel.description: I was looking around and I saw all these epic looking gameframes. How does everyone make em? Do you just use a program like photoshop, Or is there a program to make em? <--- (Stupid question, But yeah)

item.title: How to make a good gameframe?
item.dc:creator: @xxx123xxx xxx123xxx
item.description:
@xxx123xxx wrote:

[quote=“r34p4g3pk, post:5, topic:271179”][quote author=xxx123xxx link=topic=357883.msg2733632#msg2733632 date=1238901861]
yeah its photoshop.
[/quote] Instead of spending an hour making a gameframe that can have a bad effect in the end, why not cut a grame frame that takes 10 seconds, if it’s bad try another which takes another 10 seconds. There is also other editing programs you can use.[/quote]
lmao do you even know what he’s asking?
hes asking how do you make them, he suggested photoshop and i agreed with him, i dont there is a program that can match photoshop…
